        THANK_YOU_MASTER_BUT_OUR_LEAK_IS_IN                                              = 6805,  -- Thank you, Master, but our leak is in another Mog House! Bring this to me when we're back home in [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst], won't you, kupo?
        YOU_VE_FOUND_THEM_KUPO_I_KNEW_I                                                  = 6806,  -- You've found them, kupo! I knew I could count on you. That's what I tell all my moogle buddies. Why, my master is the boldest, brightest, bestest master of them all! Now we just take these, and...
