        CURRENTLY_WE_RANK_FIRST_IN_VANA_DIEL_S                                           = 7544,  -- Currently we rank first in Vana'diel's conquest, but that must not be taken for granted. We must continue our fight to remain on top.
        WE_HAD_FIRST_PLACE_IN_OUR_HANDS_BUT                                              = 7545,  -- We had first place in our hands, but we let it slip away. If we want to be ranked first in Vana'diel, each and every one of us must do their part. I look forward to hearing of your achievements.
