        I_AM_JEUNOAN_DUCAL_GUARD_MY_DUTY_IS                                              = 7555,  -- I am Jeunoan Ducal Guard, . My duty is to support the conquest efforts of Windurst, San d'Oria, and Bastok.
        PAUSE                                                                            = 7745,  -- PAUSE
        THIS_FLIGHT_IS_FULL                                                              = 7747,  -- This flight is full.
        I_GOT_NO_BUSINESS_WITH_A_FLEA_LIKE                                               = 7748,  -- I got no business with a flea like you. Get outta my face before I decide to messy-wess you up.
        YOU_RE_RIGHT_HA_HA_HA_I_KNEW                                                     = 7749,  -- You're %, right? Ha ha ha! I knew it! Just like Gilgamesh described. Lemme tell you what I gotty-wot so far.
        THE_CREEPY_WEEP_THAT_STOLE_OUR_HELMET_ISN                                        = 7750,  -- The creepy-weep that stole our helmet isn't from any large syndicate. He isn't even very famous among other pirates. He's just a simple thiefy-weef trying to pull off a big job for a big profit.
        ACCORDING_TO_THE_OWNER_OF_THAT_INN_HE                                            = 7751,  -- According to the owner of that inn, he traveled numerous timey-wimes between here and Selbina, and would sometimes talk about his plans after a few too many drinky-winks. But then one day, he just disappeared.
        AFTER_LOOKING_AT_NORG_S_NAUTICAL_LOGGY_WOGS                                      = 7752,  -- After looking at Norg's nautical loggy-wogs, I learned that the time he disappeared matches the time he must have entered our headquarters. But where he went from therey-where, I don't know.
        WA_WA_WAIT_THERE_S_SOMETHING_ELSE                                                = 7753,  -- Wa-wa-wait! There's something else.
        ONE_OF_OUR_MEN_IN_BASTOK_IS_PIECING                                              = 7754,  -- One of our men in Bastok is piecing together all the information we've gathered so far. He's hiding out in a run-down old housey-wouse in the Mines District (J-6). He should be able to give you something juicy-wuicy.
        I_THOUGHT_THAT_THIS_MIGHT_HAVE_BEEN_THE                                          = 7755,  -- I thought that this might have been the work of some large groupy-woop, but when I heard that it was just one guy...boy, was I surprisey-wised!
        I_CAN_UNDERSTAND_WANTING_TO_MAKEY_WAKE_IT                                        = 7756,  -- I can understand wanting to makey-wake it big overnight, but he should have thought a little bitty-wit longer before deciding to take us on!
        WOULD_YOU_MIND_LEAVING_ME_ALONE_I_HAVE                                           = 7757,  -- Would you mind leaving me alone? I have no time for small talk.
        YOU_ARE_ARE_YOU_NOT_I_HAVE_BEEN                                                  = 7758,  -- You are %, are you not? I have been waiting for your arrival. I do not have much time, so I will keep this quick.
        THE_DAY_OF_THE_THEFT_THERE_WERE_NUMEROUS                                         = 7759,  -- The day of the theft, there were numerous reports of a strange character wearing an even stranger helmet traveling on foot towards Zulkheim.
        I_JOURNEYED_HERE_FROM_SAN_D_ORIA_BUT                                             = 7760,  -- I journeyed here from San d'Oria, but heard nothing of such sightings on my way. This leaves the possibility that he may have turned back to Jeuno.
        I_FEEL_THAT_HE_MAY_STILL_BE_IN                                                   = 7761,  -- I feel that he may still be in the area. I am going to continue my search here.
        AND_ONE_OTHER_THING                                                              = 7762,  -- And one other thing.
        ONE_MORE_OF_US_IS_STATIONED_IN_A                                                 = 7763,  -- One more of us is stationed in a small, run-down building in the Bastok Mines (J-6). He may have some useful information.
        THE_TYPE_OF_HELMET_THAT_WAS_STOLEN_IS                                            = 7764,  -- The type of helmet that was stolen is known in the Far East as a kabuto. Many people find its design strange, but I find it quite interesting.
        YOU_RE_FINALLY_HERE                                                              = 7765,  -- You're finally here, %.
        I_VE_HEARD_OF_YOU_FROM_MY_ASSOCIATES                                             = 7766,  -- I've heard of you from my associates in Norg. As much as I would like to sit and chat with you about your adventures, we must work quickly to find our thief. I have just received a new piece of information and will be setting out shortly to investigate.
        TO_THE_NORTHEAST_OF_HERE_IS_A_PLACE                                              = 7767,  -- To the northeast of here is a place called the Palborough Mines. I've received information on several adventurers sighting a young man wearing a strangely shaped helmet journeying deep into those caves.
        THIS_IS_MORE_THAN_LIKELY_THE_SAME_CHARACTER                                      = 7768,  -- This is more than likely the same character that Sanosuke learned of in Jeuno. But why would he head to the Palborough Mines? I'm heading there myself to find out.
        I_HAVE_HEARD_THAT_THE_QUADAV_MADE_THAT                                           = 7769,  -- I have heard that the Quadav made that place into one of their strongholds. I wonder if there could be some connection...
        YOU_MAY_JOURNEY_TO_THE_MINES_WITH_ME                                             = 7770,  -- You may journey to the mines with me if you wish. When you have made your preparations, meet me there. I will be waiting.
        I_IT_S_YOU                                                                       = 7771,  -- I-it's you...
        WE_RE_TOO_LATE_HE_S_ALREADY_PASSED                                               = 7772,  -- We're too...late. He's already...passed through the...portal. The seal...on the helmet...won't hold much...longer.
        UNLESS_YOU_WANT_TO_END_UP_LIKE_ME                                                = 7773,  -- Unless you want to end up...like me, don't...touch the burning circle. It's protected...by a powerful curse.
