        SYNERGY_FURNACES_HAVE_BEEN_INSTALLED_THROUGHOUT_THE_CITY                         = 8383,  -- Synergy furnaces have been installed throughout the city for the use of all synergists. The crucible is sufficiently compact and lightweight that you can carry it with you.
