        Y_YE_VE_NO_IDEA_WHAT_THIS_MEANS                                                  = 8449,  -- Y-ye've no idea what this means to us, %! We're forever in yer debt.
        TO_HELP_YE_HELP_US_IT_LL_BE                                                      = 8450,  -- To help ye help us, it'll be me pleasure t' share all I know.
        TO_RECAP_WHAT_I_VE_ALREADY_TOLD_YE                                               = 8451,  -- To recap what I've already told ye, the cavernous maws are portals to Abyssea. But the door won't open unless ye've got one of them %.
        THAT_S_NOT_THEIR_ONLY_PURPOSE_MIND_YE                                            = 8452,  -- That's not their only purpose, mind ye.
        BESIDES_BEIN_KEYS_THEY_ALSO_SERVE_AS_ANCHORS                                     = 8453,  -- Besides bein' keys, they also serve as anchors what secure yer essence t' foreign dimensions. In simpler terms, they allow you t' stay within Abyssea, though not indefinitely.
        ONE_S_GOOD_FER_A_MINUTE_STAY_EARTH                                               = 8454,  -- One's good fer a #-minute stay (Earth time), and # of them is the most ye can hold at once. Do the math, and ye'll get the longest stretch of time folk of yer world can stay in Abyssea.
        NOW_WHAT_I_M_ABOUT_T_TELL_YE                                                     = 8455,  -- Now, what I'm about t' tell ye is deathly crucial, so take it t' heart. Stay anchored in another dimension overlong, an' what was temporary will become permanent. In other words, ye risk losin' fer good the means t' return home.
        A_BUNCH_OF_ME_MATES_AN_I_ARE                                                     = 8456,  -- A bunch of me mates an' I are livin', walkin' proof of such a tragedy.
        BUT_YE_CAN_REST_ASSURED_FER_THESE_DAYS                                           = 8457,  -- But ye can rest assured, fer % these days are worked with a safety measure. At the first sign of trouble it'll catapult ye back home safe an' sound.
        WELL_THAT_S_JUS_ABOUT_THE_BEEF_OF                                                = 8458,  -- Well, that's jus' about the beef of it. Come see me whenever ye want %, aye? I might not always have one on hand, though, as it takes a bloody long time--twenty hours, t 'be precise (Earth time)--t' infuse one with energy. Any less an' they're about as useful as skippin' stones.
