        I_DON_T_BLAME_YE_IF_YE_RE                                                        = 8505,  -- I don't blame ye if ye're feelin' reserved about meetin' this mystery man, but I assure ye, he's a real dinkum bloke.
        JUS_TAKE_YERSELF_OVER_T_THE_RENDEZVOUS_POINT                                     = 8506,  -- Jus' take yerself over t' the rendezvous point, an' he'll seek ye out. It's simple as meat pie.
        GO_WELL_BE_SEEIN_YE_AGAIN_REAL_SOON                                              = 8507,  -- Go well, %. Be seein' ye again real soon.
        WELCOME_BACK_IT_SEEMS_THE_MEETIN_WENT_WITHOUT                                    = 8508,  -- Welcome back, %. It seems the meetin' went without incident.
        I_TRUST_YE_UNDERSTAND_NOW_WHY_THE_MAN                                            = 8509,  -- I trust ye understand now why the man couldn't come t' Jeuno.
        BEIN_AN_UNDERWORLD_FIGURE_OF_SORTS_IT_WOULDN                                     = 8510,  -- Bein' an underworld figure of sorts, it wouldn't do if he were seen paradin' himself hereabouts.
        DOUBTLESS_HE_S_ALREADY_BENT_YER_EARS_BOUT                                        = 8511,  -- Doubtless he's already bent yer ears 'bout havin' been a pirate back in the day, runnin' his operations out of Elshimo.
        CONSIDERIN_HOW_WELL_TRAVELED_AN_ADVENTURER_YE_ARE                                = 8512,  -- Considerin' how well-traveled an adventurer ye are, I reckon ye already knew the man.
        BUT_I_WON_T_PROBE_YE_ON_THAT                                                     = 8513,  -- But I won't probe ye on that subject. Some things are best left untouched, t' be sure.
        I_FIND_MESELF_SAYIN_THIS_OFTEN_OF_LATE                                           = 8514,  -- I find meself sayin' this often of late, but yer aid has allowed hope t' sprout among the survivors. If ye were t' ask me if mankind's made any real progress, though, the answer would be a resoundin' no.
        THE_SURVIVORS_RE_MORE_ORGANIZED_THAN_AFORE_TRUE                                  = 8515,  -- The survivors're more organized than afore, true, but our fundamental plight be as grim as ever. The Abyssean hordes attack, an' we beat them back as best we can. An' when we're not busy fendin' off monsters, we're scrapin' up what livin' we can, foragin' fer food what can still be had.
        NONE_OF_THIS_HAS_CHANGED_AN_I_SUSPECT                                            = 8516,  -- None of this has changed, %, an' I suspect that be why ye were called out t' La Theine. Rumors of yer feats aren't like t' escape the notice of key resistance folk fer long. Soon or late, they'd look ye up, hopin' t' recruit yer aid in gettin' us out of this rut.
        HIT_THE_NAIL_FAIR_ON_THE_HEAD_DID                                                = 8517,  -- Hit the nail fair on the head, did I? I'm not the only one who sees great things in ye, %, an' fer good reason.
        ME_COMRADES_AN_I_CROSSED_OVER_T_THIS                                             = 8518,  -- Me comrades an' I crossed over t' this world, desperately searchin' fer a way t' save our home.
