        AHHH_OHHH_WHAT_A_POSITIVELY_BREATHTAKING_ARTIFACT_NOW                            = 8826,  -- Ahhh... Ohhh... What a positively breathtaking artifact. Now I have something else to absorb myself in other than the masterful teachings of Borghertz.
        MY_APOLOGIES_SIR_MADAM_GAZING_UPON_THE_INTRICACIES                               = 8827,  -- My apologies, sir/madam]. Gazing upon the intricacies of well-crafted blades and staves is a truly mesmerizing experience, and I often lose myself between their individual grains and grooves. At any rate, social custom dictates that I return this to you.
        THE_UNCOUTH_HUME_BEGRUDGINGLY_HANDS_OVER_YOUR                                    = 8828,  -- The uncouth Hume begrudgingly hands over your %.
        YES_IT_WOULD_CERTAINLY_DO_YOU_WELL_TO                                            = 8829,  -- Yes, it would certainly do you well to know my name. I go by Oboro, and as a blacksmith from the Far East, I contrive exquisite instruments of assault almost from thin air.
        WHILE_I_AM_UNDOUBTEDLY_THE_MOST_ACCOMPLISHED_SMITH                               = 8830,  -- While I am undoubtedly the most accomplished smith in my homeland, I am not an arrogant Elvaan. I have heard the rumors of Borghertz's greatness and have come to broaden my horizons under his wing.
        KNOW_YOU_OF_BORGHERTZ_THE_LEGENDARY_BLACKSMITH_REVERED                           = 8831,  -- Know you of Borghertz, the legendary blacksmith revered throughout the Far East?
        DO_YOU_KNOW_BORGHERTZ_IN_FACT_I_DO                                               = 8832,  -- Do you know Borghertz? In fact, I do...or did. Even if I did, I wouldn't tell you.
        WHAT_HE_HAS_PASSED_ON_AND_HAMMERS_AWAY                                           = 8833,  -- What!? He has passed on and hammers away happily upon the big anvil in the sky!?
        OF_COURSE_SOMEONE_OF_YOUR_INFERIOR_STATURE_WOULD                                 = 8834,  -- Of course someone of your inferior stature would not. That is all well and good, however, for we are not all destined for greatness.
        OH_WELL_LET_US_NOT_DWELL_ON_EXTRANEOUS                                           = 8835,  -- Oh well, let us not dwell on extraneous and repugnant details. Now that I have seen the almighty armament you carry...
        I_WOULD_HAVE_YOU_BEQUEATH_IT_TO_ME                                               = 8836,  -- I would have you bequeath it to me.
        IF_BORGHERTZ_IS_NOT_AVAILABLE_TO_PERFORM_THIS                                    = 8837,  -- If Borghertz is not available to perform this most ambitious of tasks, then I will gladly accept the challenge of eking out every last iota of might from your weapon.
        I_CANNOT_TELL_A_LIE_I_WILL_STAKE                                                 = 8838,  -- I cannot tell a lie. I will stake my illustrious career and own life on this claim.
        SO_WHAT_SAY_YOU                                                                  = 8839,  -- So, what say you?
        WHAT_SAY_YOU_FINE_HAVE_MY_WEAPON_YOU                                             = 8840,  -- What say you? Fine, have my weapon. You're a jerk and I hate you.
        HMPH_WELL_SUCH_IS_YOUR_LOSS_YOU_WILL                                             = 8841,  -- Hmph. Well, such is your loss. You will simply be unable to defend this city once the apocalypse descends upon it--which will happen sooner than you think.
        AH_IT_PLEASES_ME_TO_KNOW_THAT_YOU                                                = 8842,  -- Ah, it pleases me to know that you possess the intuition of a true combatant. No one would refuse the opportunity to increase the potency of the tool by which they make their living.
        I_WOULD_LIKE_NOTHING_MORE_THAN_TO_START                                          = 8843,  -- I would like nothing more than to start remolding this exquisite creation immediately, but I must first say that I cannot and will not work with anything less than the best. Consider the weapon you possess and bring me weapons that meet or exceed its power.
        AND_LET_US_SUPPOSE_YOU_ACTUALLY_PROCURE_WHAT                                     = 8844,  -- And let us suppose you actually procure what I ask of you. Will you even be able to grasp the degree to which your life will change, all thanks to my expertise? Heh heh heh, I can hardly wait.
        WHY_THE_LONG_FACE_DID_YOU_WET_YOURSELF                                           = 8845,  -- Why the long face? Did you wet yourself at the thought of losing your closest companion? No worries, I shall be waiting in this very spot when your trousers dry and your resolve hardens.
        FINALLY_COME_TO_YOUR_SENSES_AND_REALIZE_THAT                                     = 8846,  -- Finally come to your senses and realize that leaving your weapon with me is the best option you have?
        I_WAS_UNAWARE_THAT_THE_WORLD_WAS_STILL                                           = 8847,  -- I was unaware that the world was still privy to superlative works of art such as this. So grandiose is its design that one must question whether or not it was fashioned by mortal hands.
        SAY_NOTHING_OF_THE_AURA_IT_EXUDES_I                                              = 8848,  -- Say nothing of the aura it exudes. I feel as if I am conversing with an old friend simply by gazing upon it. Yes, I will indeed deign to pour my soul into improving this instrument.
        IN_ORDER_TO_DO_THAT_HOWEVER_I_REQUIRE                                            = 8849,  -- In order to do that, however, I require # . Have fun getting intimately acquainted with them as well as the beasts from which you must procure them.
        WELL_NOW_IF_I_DID_NOT_SO_LOVE                                                    = 8850,  -- Well, now...if I did not so love hearing the sound of my own voice, I would be at a loss for words. To think that I would one day come across one of the Myriad Arms of Balrahn...
        I_KNEW_IT_WAS_MY_DESTINY_TO_LAY                                                  = 8851,  -- I knew it was my destiny to lay eyes upon one when I first glanced at that ledger of arcane valuables. It seems there was a purpose in coming to this backwoods province after all.
        I_CANNOT_IN_GOOD_CONSCIENCE_TURN_DOWN_THE                                        = 8852,  -- I cannot in good conscience turn down the chance to pour my heart and soul into this magnificent creation.
        AND_TO_ASSIST_ME_IN_THIS_DIVINE_MISSION                                          = 8853,  -- And to assist me in this divine mission, you will bring me # . Now be off.
